extendedInfo.description: Dumbometer is a addictive test that measures your ability at following simple directions.Test yourself and your mates.Have tons of fun when they fail on the questions which you failed earlier.Prove that you are not a stupid.170+ steps to prove you are not Dumb (moron to genius)For clues check out dumbometer on facebook
